        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td><a href="#P250_47137">Article&nbsp;23</a>:</td>
            <td>Executive Committee: <em>1. Constitution; 2. Composition; 3. Number of members; 4. Geographical distribution; special agreements; 5. Term, limits of re-eligibility, rules of election; 6. Tasks; 7. Convocation; 8.&nbsp;Quorum, voting; 9. Observers; 10. Rules of procedure</em></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td><a href="#P282_50905">Article&nbsp;24</a>:</td>
            <td>International Bureau: <em>1. Tasks in general, Director General; 2. General information; 3. Periodical; 4. Information to countries; 5. Studies and services; 6. Participation in meetings; 7. Conferences of revision; 8. Other tasks</em></td>
        </tr>
