            <td><a href="#P297_53213">Article&nbsp;25</a>:</td>
            <td>Finances: <em>1. Budget; 2. Coordination with other Unions; 3. Resources; 4.&nbsp;Contributions; possible extension of previous budget; 5. Fees and charges; 6. Working capital fund; 7. Advances by host Government; 8. Auditing of accounts</em></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td><a href="#P333_58580">Article&nbsp;26</a>:</td>
